_sText:
I've been working on this map for a REAL long time on and off, about 2-3 months.

This is the first big map I have made where I have an actual plot.

Terrorist have taken over an oil field deep in Iran. In under a year they have built
barracks, housings, computer's, and underground tunnels. They are int the process of building
still underneath the whole city. But today the Terrorist know the CT's are coming. They will
do anything to hide what they have done, including blowing up there precious experiment.
Its the CT goal to take down the Terrorist before they can do so. Be careful, they have underground
tunnels which can quickly take them to each bomb site. Stop them dead in their tracks.

Enjoy, SO many kinks and bumps. This is in big beta. Let me know what you guys think.
